<body>
  <nav>
    <div class="container-fluid"></div><a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Equalizer</a></div>
  </nav>
  <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center align-content-center" style="margin: 10vw;">
    <p style="font-family: PlayfairDisplay;font-size: 5em;font-weight: bold;color: #d6336c;">{{user.sum}}%</p>
    <strong></strong>

    {{#if moreThan50}}
    <p class="text-center"
      style="font-size: 2em;line-height: -13.8;color: #51427d;font-weight: bold;font-family: PlayfairDisplay;">Amazing!
    </p>
    <p>You already have a lot of information. Check our blog for news and more information. <br>We would love to get in
      touch with you to discuss actions that we can do to change <strike>the future</strike> now.</p>
    {{else if score100}}

    <p class="text-center"
      style="font-size: 2em;line-height: -13.8;color: #51427d;font-weight: bold;font-family: PlayfairDisplay;">
      Contratulations!</p>
    <p>You have a good knowledge about gender equality, but information is never enough! <br>Check our blog for more
      information, follow us on our social media and letÂ´s discuss actions that we can do it to change this gender
      inequality. <br>Remember: Starts with you! ;)</p>

    {{else}}
    <p class="text-center"
      style="font-size: 2em;line-height: -13.8;color: #51427d;font-weight: bold;font-family: PlayfairDisplay;">Don't
      give up! </p>
    <p style="color: #987d86; font-family: Muli;">You are just beginning this journey towards equality and we can do it
      together. <br>Check our blog for more data and information. <br>If you have any questions, contact us on our
      social media channels. We will love to get in touch with you!</p>

    {{/if}}

<a href="/blog" class="btn btn-primary" role="button" href="" style="min-width:80%; max-width: 10px; 	border-radius: 8px;
	background-color: #d6336c; align-self-center">See our blog&nbsp;<i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i></a>


 <div class="buttons"><a class="btn btn-primary" role="button"
            href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?text=Look%20this%20quiz!%20https://worldequalizer.herokuapp.com/quiz/result/{{user._id}}" target="_blank" style=" min-width: 80%;max-width: 100%; border-radius: 8px;
	background-color: #37b24d;">Share your results!&nbsp;<i class="fa fa-whatsapp"></i></a>
        </div>

  
    <table class="table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th scope="col">Name</th>
          <th scope="col">Points</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {{#each users}}

        <tr>
          <td>{{name}}</td>
          <td>{{sum}}%</td>
        </tr>
        {{/each}}
      </tbody>
    </table>


  </div>
  <script src="assets/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
